{"tid":2307753,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有線港聞組採主及記者辭職聲明","createTime":"2020-12-01T11:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T11:33:52.000Z","uid":264958,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"eb2c708f6acd849a2bd1fa4516ddb19aa71484fc","tid":2307753,"uid":264958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:09:18.000Z","msg":"聲明<br />\n<br />\n有線新聞今日（1日）解僱約40名新聞部員工，他們大部分是資深員工，服務新聞部多年，部分在各部門過往表現突出，名單更包括專題組新聞刺針全組記者。我們多次向四名高層謝燕娜、許方輝、李臻、陳興昌要求交代裁員準則，但得到的回應只是架構重組和節省資源，更有人以「爛仔」形容同事，裁員前亦沒有知會或諮詢各部門主管，完全無視員工的付出，做法極不尊重，令人憤怒，港聞組對高層一手摧毀有線新聞部表示極度遺憾，多名員工決定即時辭職，以示不滿。在餘下的時間會緊守崗位，保持專業。<br />\n<br />\n港聞組<br />\n林穎茵（總採訪主任）<br />\n曾楚群（助理總採訪主任）<br />\n林妙茵（助理總採訪主任）<br />\n雷子樂（採訪主任）<br />\n陳婉婷（助理採訪主任）<br />\n11名港聞記者"},{"pid":"06add0cf4c9746e3b3e337e044d822e154fc28b3","tid":2307753,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139932b67d7869911c173aac2af7105fbd87266c","tid":2307753,"uid":198214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:13:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0a065633f7b210b582b9962c1c0f3121c92c80d","tid":2307753,"uid":258340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:14:42.000Z","msg":"［零成本］聲援有線！ 無人講？！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2307531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2307531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0034ba435c679b665d9e2055bd50059f9d74e2f1","tid":2307753,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:15:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZKhzjWq.gif&amp;h=11cb3317&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"5cf66558dadacff9edb54b75ae6bcb2ebadca2a0","tid":2307753,"uid":340081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"